name: GameFantasyStar
public_notice: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
StarCrazy is a play-to-earn, NFT game  built on the IoTex blockchain. 

GFS is the governance token of StarCrazy Game. 100% of the tokens are game-generated.

GFS is mainly used for in-game DAO governance, in-game bonus rewards, and ability to participate in-game payments.
